      "Title": "Action Filter ile Performans İzleme: Uygulamanızı Hızlandırın",
      "Content": "<div class='blog-content performance-blog'>\n\n<div class='performance-hero'>\n<div class='alert alert-warning border-0'>\n<div class='row align-items-center'>\n<div class='col-md-8'>\n<h2><i class='fas fa-tachometer-alt text-warning'></i> Performans İzleme ile Hızlanın</h2>\n<p class='lead mb-0'>Performans izleme, modern web uygulamalarının vazgeçilmez bir parçasıdır. Kullanıcılar yavaş yüklenen sayfalardan hızla uzaklaşır ve bu da iş kaybına neden olur. Bu yazıda Action Filter'lar kullanarak nasıl etkili performans izleme yapabileceğinizi öğreneceksiniz.</p>\n</div>\n<div class='col-md-4 text-center'>\n<div class='speed-meter'>\n<i class='fas fa-gauge-high text-warning' style='font-size: 4rem;'></i>\n<div class='speed-glow'></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='why-performance-section'>\n<h2 class='section-title'><i class='fas fa-question-circle text-danger'></i> Neden Performans İzleme Gerekli?</h2>\n\n<div class='performance-stats row'>\n<div class='col-md-4'>\n<div class='stat-card card border-danger text-center'>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<div class='stat-icon'><i class='fas fa-users text-danger'></i></div>\n<h3 class='text-danger'>40%</h3>\n<p class='mb-0'>Kullanıcı kaybı<br><small class='text-muted'>3+ saniye yükleme</small></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='col-md-4'>\n<div class='stat-card card border-warning text-center'>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<div class='stat-icon'><i class='fas fa-chart-line text-warning'></i></div>\n<h3 class='text-warning'>7%</h3>\n<p class='mb-0'>Dönüşüm kaybı<br><small class='text-muted'>1 saniyelik gecikme</small></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='col-md-4'>\n<div class='stat-card card border-success text-center'>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<div class='stat-icon'><i class='fas fa-search text-success'></i></div>\n<h3 class='text-success'>SEO</h3>\n<p class='mb-0'>Daha iyi sıralama<br><small class='text-muted'>Hızlı siteler</small></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='performance-categories row mt-4'>\n<div class='col-md-4'>\n<div class='category-card card border-primary'>\n<div class='card-header bg-primary text-white'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-smile'></i> Kullanıcı Deneyimi</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<ul class='category-list'>\n<li><i class='fas fa-clock text-danger'></i> Sayfa yükleme süresi 3 saniyeyi geçerse kullanıcıların %40'ı sayfayı terk eder</li>\n<li><i class='fas fa-chart-line text-warning'></i> 1 saniyelik gecikme, dönüşüm oranlarını %7 azaltır</li>\n<li><i class='fas fa-trophy text-success'></i> Hızlı siteler Google'da daha üst sıralarda yer alır</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='col-md-4'>\n<div class='category-card card border-info'>\n<div class='card-header bg-info text-white'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-heartbeat'></i> Sistem Sağlığı</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<ul class='category-list'>\n<li><i class='fas fa-search text-primary'></i> Hangi action'ların yavaş olduğunu bilmek gerekir</li>\n<li><i class='fas fa-exclamation-triangle text-warning'></i> Bottleneck'leri tespit etmek için veri gerekir</li>\n<li><i class='fas fa-server text-info'></i> Sistem kaynaklarının verimli kullanımı</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='col-md-4'>\n<div class='category-card card border-success'>\n<div class='card-header bg-success text-white'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-dollar-sign'></i> İş Değeri</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<ul class='category-list'>\n<li><i class='fas fa-money-bill-wave text-success'></i> Hızlı siteler daha fazla gelir getirir</li>\n<li><i class='fas fa-thumbs-up text-primary'></i> Kullanıcı memnuniyeti artar</li>\n<li><i class='fas fa-rocket text-warning'></i> Rekabet avantajı sağlar</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='filter-implementation-section'>\n<h2 class='section-title'><i class='fas fa-code text-primary'></i> Performance Filter Nasıl Çalışır?</h2>\n\n<div class='implementation-showcase'>\n<div class='card border-primary'>\n<div class='card-header bg-primary text-white'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-file-code'></i> PerformanceFilter.cs</h5>\n<div class='file-path'><small><i class='fas fa-folder'></i> Filters/PerformanceFilter.cs</small></div>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<div class='code-block'>\n<pre class='code-dark'><code class='language-csharp'>public class PerformanceFilter : ActionFilterAttribute\n{\n    private Stopwatch _stopwatch;\n\n    public override void OnActionExecuting(ActionExecutingContext context)\n    {\n        _stopwatch = Stopwatch.StartNew();\n    }\n\n    public override void OnActionExecuted(ActionExecutedContext context)\n    {\n        _stopwatch.Stop();\n        var elapsed = _stopwatch.ElapsedMilliseconds;\n        \n        // Loglama\n        var logger = context.HttpContext.RequestServices\n            .GetService&lt;ILogger&lt;PerformanceFilter&gt;&gt;();\n        logger.LogInformation($\"Action {context.ActionDescriptor.DisplayName} took {elapsed}ms\");\n        \n        // ViewBag'e ekleme\n        if (context.Controller is Controller controller)\n        {\n            controller.ViewBag.ExecutionTime = elapsed;\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n\n<div class='code-explanation mt-3'>\n<div class='row'>\n<div class='col-md-6'>\n<div class='explanation-box bg-info text-white p-3 rounded'>\n<h6><i class='fas fa-play'></i> OnActionExecuting</h6>\n<p class='mb-0'>Action çalışmadan önce Stopwatch başlatılır</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class='col-md-6'>\n<div class='explanation-box bg-success text-white p-3 rounded'>\n<h6><i class='fas fa-stop'></i> OnActionExecuted</h6>\n<p class='mb-0'>Action tamamlandıktan sonra süre hesaplanır ve loglanır</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='metrics-section'>\n<h2 class='section-title'><i class='fas fa-chart-bar text-info'></i> Performans Metrikleri</h2>\n\n<div class='metrics-grid row'>\n<div class='col-md-6'>\n<div class='metric-card card border-primary'>\n<div class='card-header bg-primary text-white'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-clock'></i> Response Time</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<div class='metric-visual'>\n<div class='metric-bar'>\n<div class='bar-fill bg-primary' style='width: 75%'></div>\n<div class='bar-label'>İsteğin yanıtlanma süresi</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class='mt-2 mb-0'>İsteğin ne kadar sürede yanıtlandığı - En kritik metrik</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='col-md-6'>\n<div class='metric-card card border-success'>\n<div class='card-header bg-success text-white'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-tachometer-alt'></i> Throughput</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<div class='metric-visual'>\n<div class='metric-bar'>\n<div class='bar-fill bg-success' style='width: 60%'></div>\n<div class='bar-label'>Saniyede işlenen istek sayısı</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class='mt-2 mb-0'>Sistem kapasitesini gösterir</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='col-md-6'>\n<div class='metric-card card border-warning'>\n<div class='card-header bg-warning text-dark'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-memory'></i> Memory Usage</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<div class='metric-visual'>\n<div class='metric-bar'>\n<div class='bar-fill bg-warning' style='width: 45%'></div>\n<div class='bar-label'>Bellek kullanımı</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class='mt-2 mb-0'>Uygulamanın bellek tüketimi</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='col-md-6'>\n<div class='metric-card card border-danger'>\n<div class='card-header bg-danger text-white'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-microchip'></i> CPU Usage</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<div class='metric-visual'>\n<div class='metric-bar'>\n<div class='bar-fill bg-danger' style='width: 30%'></div>\n<div class='bar-label'>İşlemci kullanımı</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p class='mt-2 mb-0'>CPU kaynaklarının kullanım oranı</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='best-practices-section'>\n<h2 class='section-title'><i class='fas fa-star text-warning'></i> Best Practices</h2>\n\n<div class='practices-accordion'>\n<div class='practice-item card border-warning mb-3'>\n<div class='card-header bg-warning text-dark'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-exclamation-triangle'></i> 1. Threshold Belirleme</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<p>500ms üzeri istekleri özel olarak logla</p>\n<div class='code-block'>\n<pre class='code-dark'><code class='language-csharp'>if (elapsed > 500)\n{\n    logger.LogWarning($\"Slow request detected: {elapsed}ms\");\n}</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='practice-item card border-danger mb-3'>\n<div class='card-header bg-danger text-white'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-bell'></i> 2. Alerting</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<p>Kritik yavaşlıklarda otomatik uyarı gönder</p>\n<div class='alert-example bg-light p-2 rounded'>\n<small><i class='fas fa-envelope'></i> Email, SMS veya Slack bildirimleri</small>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='practice-item card border-info mb-3'>\n<div class='card-header bg-info text-white'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-chart-line'></i> 3. Trending</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<p>Zaman içindeki performans değişimlerini takip et</p>\n<div class='trending-chart bg-light p-2 rounded text-center'>\n<small><i class='fas fa-chart-area'></i> Grafik ve trend analizi</small>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='practice-item card border-success'>\n<div class='card-header bg-success text-white'>\n<h5><i class='fas fa-user'></i> 4. User Impact</h5>\n</div>\n<div class='card-body'>\n<p>Gerçek kullanıcı deneyimini ölç</p>\n<div class='user-metrics bg-light p-2 rounded'>\n<small><i class='fas fa-stopwatch'></i> Real User Monitoring (RUM)</small>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class='conclusion-section'>\n<div class='alert alert-primary'>\n<h4><i class='fas fa-rocket'></i> Sonuç</h4>\n<p class='mb-0 lead'>Performance Filter ile uygulamanızın performansını sürekli izleyerek, kullanıcı deneyimini artırabilir ve iş değerinizi yükseltebilirsiniz. <strong>Ölçemediğiniz şeyi iyileştiremezsiniz!</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.performance-blog {\n    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n}\n\n.performance-hero {\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);\n    padding: 2rem;\n    border-radius: 15px;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\n\n.performance-hero .alert {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\n    border: none;\n    color: white;\n}\n\n.speed-meter {\n    position: relative;\n    display: inline-block;\n}\n\n.speed-glow {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 50%;\n    left: 50%;\n    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);\n    width: 100px;\n    height: 100px;\n    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,193,7,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    animation: speedPulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;\n}\n\n@keyframes speedPulse {\n    0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1); opacity: 0.7; }\n    50% { transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.3); opacity: 0.3; }\n}\n\n.performance-stats .stat-card {\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\n\n.performance-stats .stat-card:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-5px);\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n}\n\n.stat-icon {\n    font-size: 2rem;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n.category-card {\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    height: 100%;\n}\n\n.category-card:hover {\n    transform: scale(1.02);\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\n\n.category-list {\n    list-style: none;\n    padding: 0;\n}\n\n.category-list li {\n    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\n    padding: 0.5rem;\n    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.category-list li:hover {\n    background: rgba(0,123,255,0.1);\n    transform: translateX(5px);\n}\n\n.implementation-showcase .file-path {\n    opacity: 0.8;\n}\n\n.code-explanation .explanation-box {\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.code-explanation .explanation-box:hover {\n    transform: scale(1.05);\n}\n\n.metrics-grid .metric-card {\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n.metrics-grid .metric-card:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-3px);\n    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\n\n.metric-bar {\n    position: relative;\n    height: 30px;\n    background: #e9ecef;\n    border-radius: 15px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n}\n\n.bar-fill {\n    height: 100%;\n    border-radius: 15px;\n    transition: width 1s ease-in-out;\n    position: relative;\n}\n\n.bar-label {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 50%;\n    left: 10px;\n    transform: translateY(-50%);\n    color: white;\n    font-weight: 500;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n}\n\n.practices-accordion .practice-item {\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n}\n\n.practices-accordion .practice-item:hover {\n    transform: translateX(5px);\n    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\n\n/* KOD BLOĞU DÜZELTMESİ - KOYU TEMA */\n.code-block pre.code-dark {\n    background: #1e1e1e !important;\n    color: #d4d4d4 !important;\n    border: 1px solid #404040;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n    font-family: 'Consolas', 'Monaco', 'Courier New', monospace;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    overflow-x: auto;\n    box-shadow: inset 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n    margin: 0;\n}\n\n.code-block code {\n    background: transparent !important;\n    color: #d4d4d4 !important;\n    padding: 0 !important;\n    border: none !important;\n    font-family: inherit;\n}\n\n.conclusion-section .alert {\n    border-left: 5px solid #007bff;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #cce7ff 0%, #b3d9ff 100%);\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .performance-hero {\n        padding: 1rem;\n    }\n    \n    .performance-stats .col-md-4,\n    .performance-categories .col-md-4,\n    .metrics-grid .col-md-6 {\n        margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    }\n}\n</style>",
